testcase.name: getPhotoPaths should return sorted photo asset paths
photoCount should return 0 for empty photos list
getPhotoPaths should return empty list when no photos
coverImage should return null when no photos and no category cover
isValid should return false when photo categoryId doesn't match category id
coverImage should return category coverImagePath when no photos
photoCount should return correct number of photos
isValid should return false when category is invalid
coverImage should return first photo path when photos exist
isValid should return true when category and all photos are valid and match categoryId
isValid should return false when any photo is invalid
sortedPhotos should return photos sorted by position
